removeDuplicatesArrays(int[]) - Method in class com.sei.DuplicateNumber
Arrays are used to remove the duplicate numbers complexity is O(n2) Advantage - original order is maintained Disadvantage - slower o(n2)
removeDuplicatesSortingArray(int[]) - Method in class com.sei.DuplicateNumber
The input array is sorted and the unique elements are placed in the beginning Advantage - Complexity is O(nlogn) faster than previous array implementation Disadvantage - The original order is not maintained
removedupLinkedHashSet() - Method in class com.sei.DuplicateNumber
Removes the duplicate numbers by using the linked hashset which maintains the original order Advantage - maintains the original order Disadvantage - slower than hashset
